Added the `eprocessos_mock` service: a FastAPI-based record/replay proxy that mirrors every e-Processos REST endpoint used by the backend client (Vereadores, Normas, Legislaturas, Mesas, Comissões, Matérias, Sessões — including the path-traversal listing for sessões and the `presenca`/`votacao` expanders), plus a `sapl_documentos` binary proxy for councilor photos. In record mode it forwards requests upstream and persists the responses under `/data`; in replay mode it serves the cached JSON without touching the network. @ericof
